sg.edu.nus.iss.vmcs.store

Class Store

  • java.lang.Object
    • sg.edu.nus.iss.vmcs.store.Store
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    CashStore, DrinksStore

    public abstract class Store
extends java.lang.Object
    This entity object implements a generic Store. It has methods to load (add) StoreItem into the Store and release StoreItem from the Store.
    Version:
    3.0 5/07/2003
    Author:
    Olivo Miotto, Pang Ping Li
    See Also:
    CashStore, CashStoreItem, Coin, DrinksBrand, DrinksStore, DrinksStoreItem, StoreController, StoreItem, StoreObject
